  "hotspots": [
    {
      "id": "city_god_altar",
      "type": "inspect",
      "label": "香案",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 450,
      "width": 160,
      "height": 100,
      "interactionRange": 90,
      "data": {
        "text": "香案上只剩些断香和灰烬。城隍爷的泥身斑驳得厉害，半边脸都裂开了，看着比庙外的夜色还阴。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "hide_iron_box",
      "type": "inspect",
      "label": "城隍像后的暗角",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 250,
      "width": 100,
      "height": 100,
      "interactionRange": 90,
      "conditions": [
        { "flag": "got_iron_box" },
        { "flag": "box_hidden_in_temple", "op": "!=", "value": true }
      ],
      "data": {
        "text": "城隍像后头积了厚厚一层灰，砖缝里正好塞得下一只半巴掌大的铁盒。你左右看看，咬咬牙，把盒子推进去藏好了。",
        "actions": [
          { "type": "setFlag", "params": { "key": "box_hidden_in_temple", "value": true } },
          { "type": "startCutscene", "params": { "id": "temple_strangers_arrive" } }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "moonlit_wall",
      "type": "inspect",
      "label": "墙边月影",
      "x": 1100,
      "y": 600,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 180,
      "interactionRange": 130,
      "conditions": [
        { "flag": "strangers_entered_temple" },
        { "flag": "saw_standing_shadow", "op": "!=", "value": true }
      ],
      "data": {
        "text": "你屏着气，又慢慢摸回庙门口。月光从屋顶的破洞漏下来，斜斜照在墙上。墙边明明该趴着一具倒地的人影，可你看见的，却是个直挺挺站着的女人影子。\n\n你头皮一炸，连盒子都不敢再想，转身就跑，直到冲回街巷才敢喘气。今晚这事，怎么都得等天亮以后再回来看个明白。",
        "actions": [
          { "type": "setFlag", "params": { "key": "saw_standing_shadow", "value": true } },
          { "type": "setFlag", "params": { "key": "first_night_escape", "value": true } },
          { "type": "switchScene", "params": { "targetScene": "test_room_a", "targetSpawnPoint": "from_temple" } }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "hanged_woman_day2",
      "type": "inspect",
      "label": "梁下",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 600,
      "width": 140,
      "height": 140,
      "interactionRange": 100,
      "conditions": [
        { "flag": "day_2_started" },
        { "flag": "saw_hanged_woman", "op": "!=", "value": true }
      ],
      "data": {
        "text": "你抬头一看，浑身都僵了。梁上吊着一具女尸，正是昨晚那女人。她脸朝外，舌头微微伸着，眼珠子已经不会动了。\n\n你强撑着挪开眼，往城隍像后头摸——砖缝里的铁盒还在。你一把抓起来揣进怀里，头也不回地冲出了庙门。",
        "actions": [
          { "type": "setFlag", "params": { "key": "saw_hanged_woman", "value": true } },
          { "type": "startCutscene", "params": { "id": "prologue_demo_end" } }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "stone_tablet",
      "type": "inspect",
      "label": "石碑",
      "x": 300,
      "y": 350,
      "width": 80,
      "height": 120,
      "interactionRange": 80,
      "data": {
        "text": "角落里立着块旧石碑，碑文风化得只剩最后几句还能认：\"阎王岭下，阴阳交汇，城隍镇之。\"你看完只觉背后更凉了。",
        "actions": [
          { "type": "setFlag", "params": { "key": "inspected_stone_tablet", "value": true } },
          { "type": "addArchiveEntry", "params": { "bookType": "lore", "entryId": "lore_temple_history" } }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "exit_to_street_from_temple",
      "type": "transition",
      "label": "出门 (街巷)",
      "x": 700,
      "y": 850,
      "width": 120,
      "height": 80,
      "interactionRange": 70,
      "data": {
        "targetScene": "test_room_a",
        "targetSpawnPoint": "from_temple"
      }
    }
  ]
}